title: Human error
comment: Someone could lose their phone and lose control of their sleep .

title: Health
comment:
Sleep is good for your health.
But some people could use this implant to stop themselves from sleeping. Also too much sleep could be bad for your mental health and fitness.

title: Better workers
comment: People who have more sleep and are less fatigued are more likely to perform well in their jobs. This could make dangerous mistakes less likely to happen.

title: Military
comment: The bad point is that the soldiers have shown in some case to be more prepared to kill, but soliders also need good quality sleep and their schedule is very important

title: Guaranteed sleep
comment: It is very well known that sleep is good for you

title: Repairs itself
comment: This makes the implant more reliable

title: Addiction
comment: Too much of a good thing can become addictive and over controlling

title: Hackers
comment: They could know when you are asleep and rob you.

title: Scary
comment: Nothing has been proven on a large scale
